<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870803-0008 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Atlantic Research Corp.</HL><DD> 08/03/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WNEWS ATRC </IN><DATELINE> ATLANTIC RESEARCH CORP. (Alexandria, Va.)  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Robert L. Kirk was named a director of this aerospace and professional services company, succeeding Howard Laster, who died in December. Mr. Kirk is president and chief executive officer of Allied-Signal Inc.'s Allied-Signal Aerospace Co. subsidiary. </TEXT></DOC>